original: Österberg, Nils, distriktsveterinär, Motala, f. 26/11/86 i Sthlm av trädg:-mäst. Anders Gustaf Ö. o. Ulrika Sofia Andersson. G. 17 m. Ruth Blomgren. Barn: Ake f. 18, Margareta 20, Karin 21, Ingrid 26. — Stud:ex. 06, utex. fr. veter :högsk. 10. Distr :veter. i Nordimark 10, i Årjängs distr. 13. Distr :veter. i östergötl. 1. f. Motala distr. fr. 28. RVO.
translated: Österberg, Nils, district veterinarian, Motala, b. 26/11/86 in Stockholm, son of horticulturist Anders Gustaf Ö. and Ulrika Sofia Andersson. Married since 17 with Ruth Blomgren. Children: Ake b. 18, Margareta b. 20, Karin b. 21, Ingrid b. 26. Completed secondary school examination in 1906, graduated from veterinary college in 1910. District veterinarian in Nordimark from 1910, in Årjäng district from 1913. District veterinarian in Östergötland from 1921 in Motala district. Awarded the Royal Victorian Order (RVO).
